  <summary date="2019-07-23T23:01:57Z" status="Introduced in House">Protecting Our Students by Terminating Graduate Rates that Add to Debt Act or the POST GRAD Act

This bill makes graduate and professional students eligible to receive subsidized Stafford Loans under the Federal Direct Loan Program beginning on July 1, 2019. Graduate and professional students have been ineligible to receive subsidized Stafford Loans since July 1, 2012.</summary>
